## Description
The **Process Files **task allows to execute custom Java or Python code.

## Configuration
**![](data:image/png;base64,)**

- In the **Alias **field, enter the name of the task that will be displayed in the workflow.

- Click on the **Program &gt; Resource **field and select the Batch Program resource to use.

> Note

For more information, see: [Batch Program Resource Reference](/doxee-platform/docs/batch-program-resource-reference)

- *(optional) *To add a **Variable**, click  ![](data:image/png;base64,) (**Add**) and fill in the required fields.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

Enter the **Name **of the new variable.

- Enter the **Value **to assign to the new variable.
